# Particle Button Demo

Minimal, deployable demo of immersive particle button effects (inspired by [codrops/ParticleEffectsButtons](https://tympanus.net/Development/ParticleEffectsButtons/)).

## Features

- Modern, lightweight, no dependencies
- Particle burst effect on button click (works for any button)
- Responsive layout and effect
- Easy to extend for more SPA transitions

## Usage

- Click the button to see the effect.
- Edit `index.html` and add more `.particle-btn`s as needed.
- Customize the parameters in `particle-button.js` for different styles.
- Drop GIFs or images into `assets/` for further experiments.

## Deploy

- Ready for Cloudflare Pages & other static hosting.
- Just push to your repo, connect on [Cloudflare Pages](https://pages.cloudflare.com/), and go!
